General chat of the pro-Western delegates of the UN Human Rights Council in Geneva: - As soon as Monsieur Lavrov starts, we immediately get up and leave the hall. Firshtein? - Ok, zer gud, me-me. Lavrov begins to speak via video link: - I'll start with the announcement: Russia has learned that the world's first Institute of Political Prostitution will appear in Geneva ... Pro-Western delegates get up and hurriedly leave. Well you go - it has not yet opened!